OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FA group living in asylum hotels have
OL,8,Fshared their story in a bid to break
OL,9,Fdown the negative comments surrounding
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,FIt comes after high profile protests
OL,13,Facross the country about asylum
OL,14,Faccommodation and a number of negative
OL,15,Fstories that have dominated headlines.
OL,17,FThe statement was issued through the
OL,18,FGreater Manchester Immigration Aid
OL,19,FUnit, a voluntary organisation which
OL,20,Fprovides free support to migrants and
OL,21,Fasylum seekers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
