OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FThe three page 1,000 word statement
OL,8,Fattempts to explain why they came to
OL,9,Fthe UK, and how living in hotels is
OL,10,Fnot a solution any of them asked for.
OL,12,FThe letter reads: "We are a group of
OL,13,Fpeople who have come to the UK to seek
OL,14,Fsafety and have spent time living in
OL,15,Fasylum hotels while we are waiting for
OL,16,Fa decision on our asylum claim.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
