OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1761912363
OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,F"We want to communicate with people in
OL,8,Four new communities because we are
OL,9,Faware that some people in the UK are
OL,10,Fnot happy about there being asylum
OL,11,Fhotels in their area."
OL,13,FThe group was inspired to write the
OL,14,Fletter after a number of protests took
OL,15,Fplace outside of their hotel.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
