OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1761912363
OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FThe letter went on to say: "The
OL,8,Fprotests outside hotels make us feel
OL,9,Funsafe ` but we also know that the
OL,10,Fprotesters do not speak for everyone
OL,11,Fin Britain. That's why we believe it
OL,12,Fis time for people to hear our side of
OL,13,Fthe story.
OL,15,F"We are grateful that we are housed,
OL,16,Fand we do not want to complain. But we
OL,17,Fneed to share information about what
OL,18,Flife in hotels is really like because
OL,19,Fwe know that there is a lot of
OL,20,Fmisinformation about asylum hotels in
OL,21,Fthe media and on social media.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
