PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1761912363
OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,F"We want to put this right so you
OL,8,Fdon't misunderstand the situation. We
OL,9,Falso understand that people have
OL,10,Fconcerns about safety and cost, and we
OL,11,Fwant to address those ` because we
OL,12,Fbelieve that we share similar values."
OL,14,FThe statement continued: "We have come
OL,15,Fto the UK to seek safety. No one would
OL,16,Fchoose to leave their country ` we
OL,17,Fhave been forced to leave because of
OL,18,Fwar or persecution.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
