OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1761912363
OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,F"When we arrived in the UK, the
OL,8,Fgovernment put us in hotels and told
OL,9,Fus to wait while they make a decision
OL,10,Fabout our asylum claim.
OL,12,F"We tell ourselves that living in a
OL,13,Fhotel might be difficult, but it is
OL,14,Fonly temporary."
OL,16,FThe group went on to address concerns
OL,17,Fabout the cost of asylum hotels to the
OL,18,Ftax payer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
