OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FThe letter also addresses the safety
OL,8,Fconcerns many locals have raised,
OL,9,Fafter a number of isolated cases of
OL,10,Fasylum seekers committing crimes while
OL,11,Fawaiting a decision from the Home
OL,12,FOffice.
OL,14,FThe letter states: "We recognise that
OL,15,Fthere have been isolated cases of
OL,16,Fpeople seeking asylum who commit
OL,17,Fcrimes.
OL,19,F"We are as angry as you are at what
OL,20,Fthey have done, and we believe they
OL,21,Fshould face the force of the law.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
