PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1761912363
OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,F"We also know that this is a tiny
OL,8,Fproportion of the number of people who
OL,9,Fcommit crimes, and we say that you
OL,10,Fcannot judge a whole group because of
OL,11,Fwhat a very few people did wrong."
OL,13,FThe final section of the statement
OL,14,Fread: "We are grateful for the welcome
OL,15,Fwe have had from local communities `
OL,16,Fin churches, mosques, charities,
OL,17,Flibraries, community centres, ESOL
OL,18,Fclasses.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
