OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1761912363
OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,F"We have people who are looking out
OL,8,Ffor us in difficult situations, and
OL,9,Fthis helps us find a sense of
OL,10,Fbelonging. We respect the British
OL,11,Fvalues of openness and tolerance that
OL,12,Fwe have met here.
OL,14,F"Now we are here, we are committed to
OL,15,Fintegrating into British society and
OL,16,Fimproving our English, and we believe
OL,17,Fthat we have a lot to contribute.
OL,18,FAmong our members we have worked in
OL,19,Fnursing, teaching, special educational
OL,20,Fneeds, engineering, journalism, music,
OL,21,Fand more.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
