PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1761912363
OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,F"We are doing what we can to volunteer
OL,8,Fin the community. Through this we have
OL,9,Fbeen able to build connections, we
OL,10,Fhave learnt about British society, we
OL,11,Ffeel part of something.
OL,13,F"Once we get our papers, we want to
OL,14,Fwork, pay taxes and we will bring
OL,15,Fvalue to the community. We hope to be
OL,16,Fpart of a UK that will continue to be
OL,17,Fa place of fairness, tolerance and
OL,18,Fopenness. We are not here to take ` we
OL,19,Fare here to share.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
