OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1761912363
OL,3,C'We want to contribute' - Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers share open letter on life in
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,F"We hope you will see us not as
OL,8,Fstrangers, but as new neighbours who
OL,9,Fwant to live in peace and grow
OL,10,Ftogether with you."
OL,12,FA Serco spokesperson said: "Serco is
OL,13,Fresponsible for providing safe
OL,14,Faccommodation for asylum seekers,
OL,15,Fwhere we treat everyone with respect.
OL,16,FPeople staying in our hotels are
OL,17,Foffered regular, balanced meals in
OL,18,Fline with NHS nutritional guidelines."
OL,20,FThe Home Office has been approached
OL,21,Ffor comment.
